title: Diversified Recycling
story: CRT device dropped at Sarah's Trading in Northeast Atlanta
overall: Various devices with tracking devices were dropped at Diversified Recycling in Atlanta and one of their downstream recyclers, Sarah's Trading, during November & December of 2014. Later, some devices were tracked and found to be dumped in inappropriate locations.
